  </p>

  <hr width="100%" size="5" color="#212866">

  <article>
    <figure>
      <a href="https://www.pna.gov.ph/articles/1217001" target="_self">
        <img src="../media/images/cybercrimeph.jpg" alt="Cybercrime in the Philippines" class="photos">
